name: Shop Availability Airport Wise
query:
SELECT 
    ash.airport, 
    COUNT(CASE WHEN scd.expiry_date > CURRENT_DATE THEN ash.name ELSE NULL END) AS occupied_count,
    COUNT(ash.name) - COUNT(CASE WHEN scd.expiry_date > CURRENT_DATE THEN ash.name ELSE NULL END) AS available_count
FROM 
    `tabAirport Shop` ash
LEFT JOIN 
    `tabShop Contract Details` scd ON ash.name = scd.airport_shop
GROUP BY 
    ash.airport;
